text: Sir Geoffrey Cornewall was an archer from Great Britain. He was born on 7 May 1869 and died on 21 January 1951. Cornewall competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Geoffrey CornewallGeoffrey CORNEWALL == References == Category:1869 births Category:1951 deaths Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
